%% Architecture flowchart for HUD build & runtime
flowchart TD
  subgraph Build
    A[TypeScript: tsc -b tsconfig.build.json] --> B[Emit dist/main & dist/renderer]
    B --> C[Node: scripts/generate-renderer-html.js]
    C --> D[Create dist/renderer/index.html]
  end

  subgraph Runtime
    M[Electron main (dist/main/main.js)] -->|createWindow| W[BrowserWindow]
    W -->|loads file://dist/renderer/index.html| R[Renderer (app.js)]
    M -->|preload| P[Preload (dist/main/preload.js)]
    P --> R
    M --> S[Shared (dist/shared/*.js)]
    R --> S
  end

  style Build fill:#f9f,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px
  style Runtime fill:#eef,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px

  click A "https://www.typescriptlang.org/" "TypeScript"
